      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomatoes have blistered, add your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>tomato paste </strong>and <strong>sliced garlic</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 6,
